msgid "Cycle heating"
msgstr "循环加热"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Enabling nanosuit's heating mode."
msgstr "启用纳米服的加热模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanosuit'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A cluster of carefully programmed nanites designed to fully cover the body "
"and defend against external threats.  Can be activated to produce heat."
msgstr "一组精心编程的纳米机器人，设计用于完全覆盖身体并防御外部威胁。可激活以产生热量。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit (heat+)"
msgid_plural "nanosuit (heat+)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米服（加热+）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat+)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat++)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat+++)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat++++)'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Increasing nanosuit's heating mode."
msgstr "正在提升纳米服的加热模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat+)'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A cluster of carefully programmed nanites designed to fully cover the body "
"and defend against external threats.  Currently heating itself."
msgstr "一组精心编程的纳米机器人，旨在完全覆盖身体并抵御外部威胁。当前正在自我加热。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit (heat++)"
msgid_plural "nanosuit (heat++)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米服（加热++）"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit (heat+++)"
msgid_plural "nanosuit (heat+++)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米服（加热+++）"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit (heat++++)"
msgid_plural "nanosuit (heat++++)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米服（加热++++）"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanosuit (heat+++++)"
msgid_plural "nanosuit (heat+++++)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米服（加热+++++）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanosuit (heat+++++)'}.
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "Disabled nanosuit's heating mode."
msgstr "已禁用纳米服的加热模式。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech liquid compressor"
msgid_plural "nanotech liquid compressors"
msgstr[0] "纳米科技液体压缩机"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech liquid compressor'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A heavily compressed liquid storage device, it is also capable of keeping "
"its contents fresh and maintaining their temperature."
msgstr "一种高度压缩的液体存储设备，它还能保持内容物新鲜并维持其温度。"

#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid "nanotech liquid compressor d"
msgid_plural "nanotech liquid compressor ds"
msgstr[0] "纳米科技液体压缩机 d"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech liquid compressor d'}
#: .\items\gear\equipment.json
msgid ""
"A heavily compressed liquid storage device, it is basically a debug crooked "
"nail that you should not see"
msgstr "一种高度压缩的液体存储设备，基本上是一个你不应该看到的调试用弯曲钉子。"

#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "nanite multitool (small)"
msgid_plural "nanite multitool (small)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米机器人多功能工具（小型）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanite multitool (small)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanite multitool (large)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanite multitool (laser welder)'}.
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "Switch tool mode"
msgstr "切换工具模式"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanite multitool (small)'}.
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "You switch your multitool to large tools mode."
msgstr "你将多功能工具切换至大型工具模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanite multitool (small)'}
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid ""
"Nanite control unit that can mimic many tools, though some require different"
" configurations.  Currently in default form, allowing access to numerous "
"small tools."
msgstr "可模拟多种工具的纳米机器人控制单元，尽管有些需要不同的配置。当前为默认形态，允许使用众多小型工具。"

#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "nanite multitool (large)"
msgid_plural "nanite multitool (large)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米机器人多功能工具（大型）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanite multitool (large)'}.
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "You switch your multitool to laser welder mode."
msgstr "你将多功能工具切换至激光焊接器模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanite multitool (large)'}
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid ""
"Nanite control unit that can mimic many tools, though some require different"
" configurations.  Currently expanded into a larger form for bulkier tools."
msgstr "可模拟多种工具的纳米机器人控制单元，尽管有些需要不同的配置。当前扩展为更大形态以容纳更笨重的工具。"

#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "nanite multitool (laser welder)"
msgid_plural "nanite multitool (laser welder)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米机器人多功能工具（激光焊接器）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanite multitool (laser welder)'}.
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid "You switch your multitool to small tools mode."
msgstr "你将多功能工具切换至小型工具模式。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanite multitool (laser welder)'}
#: .\items\gear\multitool.json
msgid ""
"Nanite control unit that can mimic many tools, though some require different"
" configurations.  Currently configured as a laser welder."
msgstr "可模拟多种工具的纳米机器人控制单元，尽管有些需要不同的配置。当前配置为激光焊接器。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'metal nanopowder'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Incredibly finely powdered metal, it is useless for anything except use in "
"specialized nanotech turrets."
msgstr "极其精细的金属粉末，除了用于专门的纳米科技炮塔外，别无他用。"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "monomolecular dart feedstock"
msgid_plural "monomolecular dart feedstocks"
msgstr[0] "单分子飞镖原料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular dart feedstock'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "Batch of material with instructions to produce bursts of darts."
msgstr "一批带有生产飞镖爆发指令的材料。"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "monomolecular blade feedstock"
msgid_plural "monomolecular blade feedstocks"
msgstr[0] "单分子刀刃原料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular blade feedstock'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "Batch of material with instructions to produce bursts of blades."
msgstr "一批带有生产刀刃爆发指令的材料。"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "monomolecular wire feedstock"
msgid_plural "monomolecular wire feedstocks"
msgstr[0] "单分子线原料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular wire feedstock'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Batch of material with instructions to produce clouds of twisting wire.  "
"WARNING: DEADLY TO USER!"
msgstr "一批带有生产旋转线云指令的材料。警告：对使用者致命！"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid "xl monomolecular wire feedstock"
msgid_plural "xl monomolecular wire feedstocks"
msgstr[0] "超大单分子线原料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'xl monomolecular wire feedstock'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Large block of material for producing large clouds of monomolecular wire.  "
"WARNING: DEADLY TO USER!"
msgstr "用于产生大片单分子线云的大型材料块。警告：对使用者致命！"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "nanotech ammo core (wire)"
msgid_plural "nanotech ammo core (wire)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术弹药核心（线）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (wire)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (dart)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (blade)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)'}.
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
