msgstr "重置并清空"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (wire)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (dart)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (blade)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)'}.
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "You clear and reset your ammo core."
msgstr "你清空并重置了弹药核心。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (wire)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (dart)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (blade)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech ammo core'}
#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid ""
"An automated ammo production unit designed to process feedstock into usable "
"ammo as needed, complete with integrated power source.  Unfortunately, it "
"needs to be manually reset when emptied, and cannot be refilled by hand."
msgstr "一种自动弹药生产单元，设计用于根据需要将原料加工成可用弹药，并配有集成电源。不幸的是，清空后需要手动重置，且无法手动重新填充。"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "nanotech ammo core (dart)"
msgid_plural "nanotech ammo core (dart)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术弹药核心（飞镖）"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "nanotech ammo core (blade)"
msgid_plural "nanotech ammo core (blade)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术弹药核心（刀刃）"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)"
msgid_plural "nanotech ammo core (deathcloud)s"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术弹药核心（死亡云）"

#: .\items\gear\nanotech_mags.json
msgid "nanotech ammo core"
msgid_plural "nanotech ammo cores"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术弹药核心"

#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid "nanotech blade"
msgid_plural "nanotech blades"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术刀刃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech blade'}
#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid ""
"An incredibly sharp blade of active nanites with a small handle.  Compresses"
" itself into the handle when not in use."
msgstr "一把带有小握柄、由活性纳米机器人构成的极其锋利的刀刃。不使用时，它会自行压缩进握柄中。"

#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid "nanotech dagger"
msgid_plural "nanotech daggers"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术匕首"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech dagger'}
#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid ""
"An incredibly sharp blade of active nanites with a small handle.  Compresses"
" itself into the handle when not in use.  In addition to the typical blade, "
"it can project blades around your fingers to be used as a claw or punching "
"dagger."
msgstr ""
"一把带有小握柄、由活性纳米机器人构成的极其锋利的刀刃。不使用时，它会自行压缩进握柄中。除了典型的刀刃外，它还能在你的手指周围投射刀刃，用作爪或拳刺。"

#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid "nanotech spear"
msgid_plural "nanotech spears"
msgstr[0] "纳米技术长矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech spear'}
#: .\items\gear\weapons.json
msgid ""
"An incredibly sharp spike of active nanites on a long handle, it contains "
"small but powerful boosters for sweeping strikes as a staff as well.  "
"Compresses itself into a small tube when not in use."
msgstr ""
"一根安装在长柄上的、由活性纳米机器人构成的极其锋利的尖刺，它还包含小型但强大的助推器，用于作为长棍进行横扫攻击。不使用时，它会自行压缩成一个小管。"

