#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech door"
msgstr "纳米科技门"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech door'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A very durable barrier composed of nanites acting as a door, it also "
"contains a fine mesh that acts as a window."
msgstr "一种由纳米机器人构成的非常耐用的屏障，用作门，同时包含一层细密的网格，起到窗户的作用。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech iris"
msgstr "纳米科技虹膜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech iris'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A highly durable iris composed of nanites, this blocks sight while also "
"acting as a combination of door and armor."
msgstr "一种由纳米机器人构成的高度耐用的虹膜，既能阻挡视线，又能兼具门和装甲的功能。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech boat coating"
msgstr "纳米科技船只涂层"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech boat coating'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"An outer coating of nanites that work together to seal out water while also "
"providing another layer of protection."
msgstr "一层纳米机器人外部涂层，协同工作以防水，同时提供额外的保护层。"

