#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech rifle turret'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "A nanotech rifle adapted for vehicular usage."
msgstr "一种适用于车辆使用的纳米科技步枪。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech SMG turret"
msgstr "纳米科技冲锋枪炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech SMG turret'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "A nanotech smg adapted for vehicular usage."
msgstr "一种适用于车辆使用的纳米科技冲锋枪。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech aisle"
msgstr "纳米科技通道"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech aisle'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "A nanotech aisle, capable of assisting with lifting nearby objects."
msgstr "一种纳米科技通道，能够协助提升附近的物体。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "nanotech roof"
msgstr "纳米科技车顶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech roof'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "A nanotech roof that is capable of interfacing with a turret."
msgstr "一种能够与炮塔交互的纳米科技车顶。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech solar panel"
msgstr "纳米科技太阳能板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech solar panel'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large sheet of nanites arranged to capture sunlight and convert it to "
"electrical energy."
msgstr "一大片排列好的纳米机器人，用于捕捉阳光并将其转化为电能。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech passive plating"
msgstr "纳米科技被动装甲板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech passive plating'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Nanites formed into a self-reinforcing mesh designed to reduce incoming "
"damage."
msgstr "纳米机器人形成的自增强网格，旨在减少受到的伤害。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech active plating"
msgstr "纳米科技主动装甲板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech active plating'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Nanites formed into a highly active mesh designed to shred anything they "
"collide with."
msgstr "纳米机器人形成的高度活跃网格，旨在粉碎任何与其碰撞的物体。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech compression tank (500L)"
msgstr "纳米科技压缩罐（500升）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech compression tank (500L)'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Collection of nanites formed into a hollow sphere with a complex mechanism "
"to compress and decompress liquid to extreme levels."
msgstr "由纳米机器人组成的空心球体，配备复杂机制，可将液体压缩或解压至极端水平。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech 'shoggoth' storage node"
msgstr "纳米技术'修格斯'存储节点"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "nanotech 'shoggoth' storage node"}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large blob of nanites with an AI, it actively branches out pseudopods to "
"grasp items held near it and supports them as optimally as possible"
msgstr "一大团搭载人工智能的纳米机器人，它会主动伸出伪足抓取附近的物品，并以最优方式支撑它们。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech crafting node"
msgstr "纳米技术制作节点"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech crafting node'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large blob of nanites with an AI, it actively branches out pseudopods to "
"assist with crafting efforts performed nearby.  Additionally, it will act as"
" most tools upon command."
msgstr "一大团搭载人工智能的纳米机器人，它会主动伸出伪足协助附近的制作工作。此外，它还能根据指令充当大多数工具使用。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech fridge"
msgstr "纳米技术冰箱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech fridge'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Collection of nanites formed into a hollow container, a large portion of "
"their power is devoted to maintaining a cool temperature, leading to them "
"being immobile and blocking passage."
msgstr "由纳米机器人组成的空心容器，其大部分能量用于维持低温，导致无法移动并会阻挡通道。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech freezer"
msgstr "纳米技术冷冻柜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech freezer'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Collection of nanites formed into a hollow container, a large portion of "
"their power is devoted to maintaining a frozen temperature, leading to them "
"being immobile and blocking passage."
msgstr "由纳米机器人组成的空心容器，其大部分能量用于维持冰冻温度，导致无法移动并会阻挡通道。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "installed nanofactory MK I"
msgstr "已安装的纳米工厂 MK I"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'installed nanofactory MK I'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large and bulky prototype nanofactory sitting on a frame somehow not "
"functioning properly"
msgstr "一个庞大笨重的原型纳米工厂安装在框架上，但不知为何无法正常运作。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "installed nanofactory MK II"
msgstr "已安装的纳米工厂 MK II"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'installed nanofactory MK II'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large and bulky nanofactory sitting on a frame somehow not functioning "
"properly."
msgstr "一个庞大笨重的纳米工厂安装在框架上，但不知为何无法正常运作。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech power generator"
msgstr "纳米技术发电机"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech anima"
msgstr "纳米技术动力核心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech anima'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A mass of nanites programmed to locate mechanical power systems and "
"interface with them to provide mechanical power."
msgstr "一团经过编程的纳米机器人，用于定位机械动力系统并与之对接以提供机械动力。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech control pod"
msgstr "纳米技术控制舱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech control pod'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A large blob of nanites you can enter, it acts as a combined control system,"
" chair, and camera control system all in one."
msgstr "一大团可进入的纳米机器人，它集控制系统、座椅和摄像头控制系统于一体。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech shock mesh"
msgstr "纳米技术防震网"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech shock mesh'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A series of straps attached to the seat, intended to fasten together after "
"going over your shoulders and hips and between your legs."
msgstr "一系列固定在座椅上的绑带，设计用于跨过肩部、臀部及双腿之间后扣紧。"

#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid "nanotech sensor array"
msgstr "纳米技术传感器阵列"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech sensor array'}
#: .\items\vehicle\vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Advanced nanotech sensor array with basic armor, can transmit video to a "
"camera control system or a nanotech control pod."
msgstr "配备基础装甲的先进纳米技术传感器阵列，可将视频传输至摄像头控制系统或纳米技术控制舱。"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "nanotech floor"
msgstr "纳米技术地板"

#. ~ Description for nanotech floor
#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A perfectly smooth floor with matching roof composed of nanites, can easily "
"withstand almost anything."
msgstr "由纳米机器人构成的完美光滑地板及匹配天花板，可轻松承受几乎任何冲击。"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "sssssssss!"
msgstr "嘶嘶嘶嘶嘶！"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "whump!"
msgstr "砰！"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "nanotech wall"
msgstr "纳米技术墙壁"

#. ~ Description for nanotech wall
#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid ""
"An incredibly durable and perfectly uniform wall composed of nanites.  More "
"than capable of supporting a roof, as well as keeping out most practically "
"anything."
msgstr "由纳米机器人构成的极其耐用且完全均匀的墙壁。不仅能支撑屋顶，还能阻挡几乎所有实际威胁。"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "sealed nanotech iris"
msgstr "密封式纳米技术虹膜门"

#. ~ Description for sealed nanotech iris
#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A sealed iris composed of nanites, this door is capable of withstanding "
"nearly anything."
msgstr "由纳米机器人构成的密封虹膜门，这道门能够承受几乎任何冲击。"

#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid "open nanotech iris"
msgstr "开启纳米科技虹膜"

#. ~ Description for open nanotech iris
#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid ""
"An opened iris composed of nanites, this door is capable of withstanding "
"nearly anything."
msgstr "由纳米机器人组成的开启式虹膜，这扇门几乎能抵御任何冲击。"

#. ~ Description for nanotech roof
#: .\mapstuff\terrain.json
msgid ""
"A perfectly smooth roof composed of nanites, can easily withstand almost "
"anything."
msgstr "由纳米机器人构成的完美光滑屋顶，能轻松抵御几乎所有冲击。"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "You shouldn't see this. nano_turret_pistol_weapon"
msgstr "你不该看到这个。nano_turret_pistol_weapon"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "You shouldn't see this. nano_turret_shredder_weapon"
msgstr "你不该看到这个。nano_turret_shredder_weapon"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "You shouldn't see this. nano_turret_rifle_weapon"
msgstr "你不该看到这个。nano_turret_rifle_weapon"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "You shouldn't see this. nano_turret_smg_weapon"
msgstr "你不该看到这个。nano_turret_smg_weapon"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech pistol turret'}
#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid ""
"A shimmering pool of liquid metal with a small barrel sticking out, this "
"turret specializes in accuracy, though it lacks in raw power."
msgstr "一滩闪烁的液态金属，伸出一根小口径枪管，这座炮塔专精于精准射击，但威力有所欠缺。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech shredder turret'}
#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid ""
"A shimmering pool of liquid metal with a wide barrel sticking out, this "
"turret specializes in power, though it lacks in accuracy and range."
msgstr "一滩闪烁的液态金属，伸出一根宽口径枪管，这座炮塔专精于威力，但精准度和射程有所不足。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech rifle turret'}
#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid ""
"A shimmering pool of liquid metal with a long barrel sticking out, this "
"turret specializes in accuracy, though it lacks in raw power."
msgstr "一滩闪烁的液态金属，伸出一根长枪管，这座炮塔专精于精准射击，但威力有所欠缺。"

#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid "nanotech smg turret"
msgid_plural "nanotech smg turrets"
msgstr[0] "纳米科技冲锋枪炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nanotech smg turret'}
#: .\monsters\turrets.json
msgid ""
"A shimmering pool of liquid metal with a short barrel sticking out, this "
"turret specializes in speed, though it lacks in range and sustainability."
msgstr "一滩闪烁的液态金属，伸出一根短枪管，这座炮塔专精于射速，但射程和持续作战能力有所不足。"
